sequenceDiagram
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant Hook as Hook Script
    participant FS as File System
    
    Note over CC: Hook Trigger Event
    CC->>Hook: stdin: JSON input
    Note over Hook: Read stdin<br/>Parse JSON
    Hook->>FS: Read project files<br/>(if needed)
    FS-->>Hook: File contents
    Note over Hook: Apply logic<br/>Check patterns
    Hook->>CC: stdout: JSON response
    Note over CC: Parse response<br/>Apply decision
    
    alt Blocking Hook (allow/block/modify)
        Note over CC: Continue or block<br/>based on decision
    else Non-Blocking Hook (context injection)
        Note over CC: Augment context<br/>continue execution
    end
